messages.text: Like eyes reflected in car headlights
Isn’t it supposed to be dark out there?
Mhm on the road and around
How can your father drive then
But it’s starting to freak me out
The landscape. It’s sort of silvery white and flashing by
The kind of setting you’d expect to see an old haunted mansion in
Haha too many Series of Unfortunate Events for you
It looks like there could be things out there. Creatures
Probably some deer or a badger
Must be many of them around
Hold on I’m trying to see
Oh haha you had me freaked out for a sec
So it’s a stray dog. Or not even stray
But I’ve seen it three times now
Think. The same dog. Three times. We’re doing 70 on a freeway
But didn’t he die a couple of months ago...
He looks slightly different, greenish eyes and bigger
I don’t know. We put him to sleep because he had a weird disease and it cost too much to operate. Maybe he wants revenge
Come on that’s just nonsense. Must be a trick of the moonlight
How can he do that if you’re driving
I dunno but it’s him I swear
Tell your mom or your brother. Does anyone else see him?
My brother is glued to his ipad, oblivious
I tried to tell my mom she says I’m seeing things
She’s cranky cause I woke her up
See well maybe you just miss him that’s all
What? Hey! Don’t just disappear like that
My brother SAW HIM as well! Nearly threw the ipad through the window
It’s getting hard to see with the fog
We’re trying to convince my parents that we saw him
Well they won’t believe you anyway
I’ve never seen my Mom lose speech
Even dad, he’s in shock I can tell
What are you going to do?
What? No don’t, what if it’s dangerous?
But you said he looks angry!
What if it’s an actual ghost or werewolf??
Or some alien using your old dog’s form?
DON’T GO looking for him! Haven’t you seen ANY horror movie?
He was the sweetest dog though
Wow it’s very different to actually be out
Oh god you’re all going to get killed or eaten
Or maybe...there’s something green a bit farther away!!
Oh no I don’t want to be part in your psycho experience...
Aah! I can’t stand not being part of it though. WHAT is going on? Have you found him???
No, no sign of him at all. Disappeared
There was an accident on the freeway
A huge pile up of cars
OMG it’s horrible. Chunks of cars everywhere. Smoke, fire! People screaming
Our car is ok but there’s like 20 cars all smashed into each other
Just turned on the news. I see it. Oh wow you were so lucky!! There must be people dead in there. Are you all ok?
He wasn’t mad, he was just trying to say something
We would have all died in that accident
If we hadn’t stopped to look for him
